<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Privacy Policy - GreenTech Ride' }) %>

<main class="container-1300 mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:py-20">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
    Last Updated: November 16, 2025
  </p>

  <section class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
    <p>
      Your privacy is critically important to us. This policy outlines how GreenTech Ride collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users of the Platform.
    </p>

    <!-- 1. Information Collection -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 pt-4 border-t">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
      <li>**Personal Identification Information**: Name, email address, phone number, and physical address collected during registration.</li>
      <li>**Financial Information**: Payment details (processed securely by third-party gateways; we do not store full card numbers).</li>
      <li>**Vehicle & Document Data**: Driving license, government ID, vehicle RC, and insurance papers (required for verification).</li>
      <li>**Location Data**: GPS location data collected from the Vehicle during the rental period for safety and tracking purposes.</li>
      <li>**Usage Data**: Information about how you use the Platform, such as pages visited and time spent.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- 2. How We Use Collected Information -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 pt-4 border-t">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
      <li>To process transactions and manage your rental bookings.</li>
      <li>For identity verification and fraud prevention, particularly using document data.</li>
      <li>To improve customer service and personalize the user experience.</li>
      <li>To track vehicle location during rentals for security and emergency response.</li>
      <li>To send periodic emails regarding your bookings or policy updates.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- 3. Data Protection -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 pt-4 border-t">3. Data Protection and Security</h2>
    <p>
      We adopt appropriate data collection, storage, and processing practices and security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your personal information, document files, and data stored on our Platform.
    </p>

    <!-- 4. Third-Party Sharing -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 pt-4 border-t">4. Sharing Your Personal Information</h2>
    <p>
      We do not sell, trade, or rent users' personal identification information to others. We may share general demographic information (not linked to any personal identification) with our business partners for marketing purposes.
    </p>
    <p>
      **Mandatory Sharing**: We will share your information, including location and document data, with the relevant insurance providers and law enforcement agencies if required by law or in the event of an accident, theft, or legal investigation.
    </p>
  </section>
</main>

